OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry day with some good
OL,6,Fsunny spells, especially for Shetland.
OL,7,FHowever the odd light afternoon shower
OL,8,Fnot to be ruled out for Orkney.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,11,Fsunny spells, but turning cloudier for
OL,12,FShetland. The rest of the night will
OL,13,Fbe dry and breezy with cloud becoming
OL,14,Fwidespread.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA cloudy but mostly dry
OL,17,Fmorning ahead of patchy light rain
OL,18,Fspreading north in the afternoon.
OL,19,FStrong southeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
