OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,7,For a few spells of rain, some of which
OL,8,Fmay be on the heavy side. Risk of sea
OL,9,Fmist and fog at times.
